sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Container, Typography, Paper, Stack, Button, Card, CardContent, CardHeader, Divider, Box, List, ListItem, ListItemIcon, ListItemText, } from '@mui/material'; import CheckCircleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CheckCircle'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; const formatCurrency = (amount) => amount == null ? 'N/A' : `$${amount.toLocaleString(undefined, { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 })}`; export default function Pricing() { const questionsPricing = useSelector((state) => state.responses?.questionsPricing || 0); const serviceCatalogPricing = useSelector((state) => state.responses?.serviceCatalogPricing || 0); const bronzeMonthly = questionsPricing; const silverMonthly = questionsPricing + serviceCatalogPricing; const bronzeAnnual = bronzeMonthly * 12; const silverAnnual = silverMonthly * 12; return ( Pricing Plans Choose the right plan for your accounting needs {/* Bronze Tier */} {formatCurrency(bronzeMonthly)} per month or {formatCurrency(bronzeAnnual)} annually Includes: {/* Silver Tier */} POPULAR {formatCurrency(silverMonthly)} per month or {formatCurrency(silverAnnual)} annually Includes everything in Bronze, plus: {/* Info Section */} How Pricing Works Bronze Plan: Monthly pricing calculated based on your responses to the questionnaire on the Questions page. Silver Plan: Monthly pricing that includes both questionnaire responses AND any additional services you select from the Services page. Note: These plans do not include one-time setup or advisory fees, which are billed separately. ); }
